Package hk.edu.hkmu.lib

Class AuthenticateLibLDAP

java.lang.Object
hk.edu.hkmu.lib.AuthenticateLibLDAP
public class AuthenticateLibLDAP
extends java.lang.Object
This class serve to authenticate users against OUHK LIB UAS LDAP server. And, the class can check if users authenticated against UAS are valid users of certain by the access list checking.
Since:
10 Mar 2020
Version:
1.0
Author:
Wai-yan NG, wwyng@ouhk.edu.hk

    • authenticate

      public void authenticate​(java.lang.String allowUserList, java.lang.String from)
      Authenticate against the LIB UAS (host defined in config.txt). User name and password must be set before calling this.
      Parameters:
      allowUserList - The list of allowed users in addition to authentication against UAS.
      from - Onto which system users are going to login.
